                              *********************** ECOMMERCE BASIR AMAZONA PROJECT *************************
                              
 1- DATA.JS CONTAIN  ALL PRODUCTS  LINK  https://github.com/basir/amazona/commit/7d86fd3398d50f84be8acde980cbb039c4c5df22
 2- IMPORT FILE IN APP.JS
 3- PRODUCT.JS MAPPING WITH DATA >>>>>   IMPORT PRODUCT.JS IN APP.JS AND MAKE TO PRODUCT.JS INSIDE DATA OF PRODUCTS MAP SEND KEY {ID} AND {DATA}
 4-IN PRODUCT.JS MAKE CARD TO PRODUCT AND IMPORT RATING.JS IN IT AND IN PRODUCT.JS SEND RATING OF PRODUCT IN PROPS TO RATING.JS AND NUMVIEWS
 5- IN RATING.JS MAKE DIFFERENT STARS VIEWS if :
 
  star number one >>>>>> * if product have rating >1 show tam star if rating<1 show half star 
   star number 2 >>>>>> * if product have rating >2 show tam star if rating<1.5 show half star 
    star number 4 >>>>>> * if product have rating >1 show tam star if rating<1 show half star 
     star number 5 >>>>>> * if product have rating >1 show tam star if rating<1 show half star 
     
     link https://github.com/basir/amazona/commit/7d86fd3398d50f84be8acde980cbb039c4c5df22
     like this  <span>
        <i
          className={
            rating >= 1
              ? 'fa fa-star'
              : rating >= 0.5
              ? 'fa fa-star-half-o'
              : 'fa fa-star-o'
          }
        ></i>
      </span>
      <span>
        <i
          className={
            rating >= 2
              ? 'fa fa-star'
              : rating >= 1.5
              ? 'fa fa-star-half-o'
              : 'fa fa-star-o'
          }
        ></i>





